Text:
You really scare me , you really are a wild man . 
And I don't want to be too cheeky to you in case you track me down pick my lock  , beat me , rape me , blow me up then eat me . Or you might just send a hitman . 
But one things for sure , you have the scariest uploads I have seen in a long while .

lol , would be good stuff for a survival situation :)  

This is for information purposes only.

It might also be cool to learn how to convert explosive missiles into model rockets, in case peace broke out before we had a chance to use them all.

I'm just sayin'...
